data.description: OPEN HOUSE 12/16.. Buy your family a house for the holidays.  Seller willing to help with rate buy down. STOP THE CAR.... This amazing house is priced to sell... This Home features 3-bed 2-bath open floor plan with newer paint, flooring and carpet throughout. Newer kitchen cabinets, appliances, newer windows and ceiling fans. Tile throughout kitchen, family room and hallway. The kitchen is clean and a good size.  The backyard is ready for entertaining. The front of the house has great curb appeal and you will have pride of ownership pulling up to this home. Conveniently located near shopping, dining and schools. Close to freeways as well. Come to the open House, THIS HOUSE WILL NOT LAST.. Do not hesitate call with questions.
